CREATE USER IF NOT EXISTS "SA" SALT '0082924ec4e40700' HASH '09c27ff74a387d755713de1f07b27dc6f4c2df1397dde3a2211ec7f58569230d' ADMIN;         
CREATE CACHED TABLE "PUBLIC"."CUSTOMERS"(
    "ID" BIGINT GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY(START WITH 1 RESTART WITH 37) NOT NULL,
    "ACTIVE" BOOLEAN,
    "ADDRESS" CHARACTER VARYING(255),
    "CPF" CHARACTER VARYING(255),
    "EMAIL" CHARACTER VARYING(255),
    "NAME" CHARACTER VARYING(255),
    "PHONE" CHARACTER VARYING(255)
);         
ALTER TABLE "PUBLIC"."CUSTOMERS" ADD CONSTRAINT "PUBLIC"."CONSTRAINT_6" PRIMARY KEY("ID");    
-- 5 +/- SELECT COUNT(*) FROM PUBLIC.CUSTOMERS;               
CREATE CACHED TABLE "PUBLIC"."PRODUCTS"(
    "ID" BIGINT GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY(START WITH 1 RESTART WITH 37) NOT NULL,
    "ACTIVE" BOOLEAN,
    "ANIMAL_TYPE" CHARACTER VARYING(255),
    "BRAND" CHARACTER VARYING(255),
    "COST_PRICE" FLOAT(53),
    "MINIMUM_STOCK" INTEGER,
    "NAME" CHARACTER VARYING(255),
    "SALE_PRICE" FLOAT(53),
    "STOCK" INTEGER,
    "WEIGHT" FLOAT(53)
);       
